{"tid":1541833,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭打爆建制內部","createTime":"2019-09-04T16:19:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T16:40:47.000Z","uid":304414,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8783a4f99b4e636acddef201e2f4a9b6cfa4e055","tid":1541833,"uid":304414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:19:12.000Z","msg":"CCTVB報導:<br />\n<br />\n而林鄭月娥發表講話前，有份同她會面的民建聯議員有不同看法。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯區議會(二)議員李慧琼稱：「如果任何措施都沒有，困局繼續下去，我想大家都很辛苦。你問我其實是遲的，大家都希望困局早日解決，永遠都是如果你想解困局，都要有人走出一步。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">民建聯新界東議員葛珮帆指：「今日特首指撤回這條例，我們都收到一些市民表示憤怒，認為這等同向惡勢力低頭等等。」</span><br />\n<br />\n據了解，<span style=\"color: red;\">部分工聯會議員不滿意林鄭月娥只讓步，而不提出其他強硬措施，變相示弱，在會面中途提早離場。</span><br />\n<br />\n建制就未有炸彈都自爆割蓆，手足們核彈都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc3ba42f439b6287dbada218f574bfbabd2c43eb","tid":1541833,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:21:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi